OL,5, Children as young as eight are being   
OL,6, strip-searched by the police, according
OL,7, to a report showing "deeply concerning"
OL,8, and "widespread" failures.             
OL,10,FIt also found some children were       
OL,11,Fstrip-searched in the back of police   
OL,12,Fvans, in schools and outside fast-food 
OL,13,Foutlets.                               
OL,15,FThe report by Children's Commissioner  
OL,16,FDame Rachel de Souza showed 2,847      
OL,17,Fchildren were searched in England and  
OL,18,FWales from 2018 to mid-2022.           
OL,20,FThe National Police Chiefs' Council    
OL,21,Fwill "carefully consider" the findings.
